0.000Z","msg":"黨既下一步應該就係猶山櫛考啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db10b11f9f71f9e8763165e626bf232c055b7161","tid":1593360,"uid":253016,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"03c3d79b9fda40562deb7b6d8e1998a62416d077","tid":1593360,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4bca5948e94b511f63e515c9da5b826fd4a4a3d","tid":1593360,"uid":61882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:09:59.000Z","msg":"傻啦<br />\n開唔到源咪節流囉<br />\n要人口唔好咁老化<br />\n少啲老人咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:13:21.000Z","msg":"所以中國人真係無得輸，殺老人家呢啲事民主國家一定唔容許"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:37:21.000Z","msg":"就係班死老野擁護共產黨搞到今時今日咁<br />\n共產黨要節流我地一定支持"},{"pid":"5d0a765164ffea3773a204cc7869ed5842c2f4ce","tid":1593360,"uid":153239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:37:40.000Z","msg":"你自己8964都殺唔少年青人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f62379725f6f869440569b477c867bd28ac5a68","tid":1593360,"uid":259582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:40:51.000Z","msg":"香港都有人口老化問題 而家咁嘅時勢點生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a055bb18afa71378d8a70e212a6534f4ad3af5cb","tid":1593360,"uid":276989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:50:34.000Z","msg":"出生率係無錯到架<br />\n只不過飲完三鹿奶粉等元素週期表，淘汰咗1／3，應該要計算出生後1年既存活率先有用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBTW 2025千人計劃已經超越美國，使鬼等到2050，垃圾學者"},{"pid":"08ad5b8927d5bacc71a6ec1a89c30dfaeac2719f","tid":1593360,"uid":323360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:54:03.000Z","msg":"維隱控制人思想為首要目標，教育醫療做次要<br />\n一啲道德都冇，生幾多都冇用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18f4a332bf9b863feac28a5479e455b574266982","tid":1593360,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:55:05.000Z","msg":"其實中國人口減小先係正路<br />\n<br />\n以前做世界工廠, 先需要咁多人口<br />\n<br />\n家陣工廠全部搬走, 如果繼續咁多人口, 就會大量人失業, 然後造反<br />\n古代黃巾起義, 太平天國起義, 都是太多人失業, 集埋一齊再起義"},{"pid":"af8c0a5c32ec12345ef52c64762e97c3abeff431","tid":1593360,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:04:47.000Z","msg":"中共70年黎都殺左成億中國人啦<br />\n唔差在殺埋個幾百萬件老人家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f908e2931809b36d4b57c853aea247bfebce5f","tid":1593360,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:12:33.000Z","msg":"我記得有篇俄佬報導<br />\n用曬數據去分析，推測中國其實無咁多人口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}